channel.description:
Hey guys, I am doing a free response worksheet for my calc class. I can't figure out this question. The question asks
State what would be graphically true if p(x)=g(x). Then, state for how many x-values p(x)=g(x)
A picture of the graph of g(x) is given, which I can provide if needed. And p(x)=-√(x+4)+1
Any ideas?
